586
00:59:27,667 --> 00:59:28,958
You're not here.

587
00:59:30,292 --> 00:59:31,500
I'm all alone.

588
00:59:33,083 --> 00:59:38,000
You're not a man, a husband,
a father, you're nothing. I'm alone.

589
00:59:41,417 --> 00:59:43,250
Who are you?

590
