630
01:06:42,250 --> 01:06:45,000
Yes, sometimes he brought me things.

631
01:06:45,375 --> 01:06:48,375
Thank you for coming with me Gonzalo.
It was very kind of you.

632
01:06:49,042 --> 01:06:50,958
Would you mind
