737
01:16:51,333 --> 01:16:52,375
It's okay.

738
01:16:52,542 --> 01:16:53,542
Leave it there.

739
01:16:53,708 --> 01:16:55,083
- Bollocks.
- Shit.

740
01:16:55,875 --> 01:16:56,958
Is it broken?

741
01:16:57,083 --> 01:16:58,542
Leave it.
Let's go.

742
01:17:28,375 --> 01:17:29,625
Jesus!

743
